		<title>Is Bitcoin Still the First Crypto Beginners Should Buy in 2026?</title>
		<link>https://ventureburn.com/is-bitcoin-still-the-first-crypto-beginners-should-buy-in-2026/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Staff Reporter]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 16 Jun 2026 14:01:45 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Cryptocurrency]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[News]]></category>
